Crystal cove cabins



The houses on the far side of PCH are new. The cabins below them are much older; the residents were recently evicted to make way for some kind of luxury hotel development.
Taken Monday, September 03, 2001, 04:56:20pm.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 929kb
Technical details: Olympus C700UZ, 1/200s @ F7.0, ISO 100, 200mm
